<p>This fragrant drink is as lively as the thoroughbred racehorse Thomas Shelby buys, which he names Grace's Secret after his wife. </p>

<p>He hires the seductive May Fitz Carleton (Charlotte Riley) to train her, and a love triangle ensues.</p>

<p>For 1 glass – Preparation: 5 minutes</p>

<p>Pour the gin, vermouth, elderflower liqueur and bitters into a mixing glass filled with ice. </p>

<p>Mix using a long, slim spoon. Strain into a cocktail glass without ice. Squeeze the lemon twist into the glass before using it for garnish.</p>

